{"tid":12612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人黎LIHKG 係因為LIHK","createTime":"2016-11-29T17:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T17:37:28.000Z","uid":43331,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae5f80a08e9340084eda9278470e1e2075fa229","tid":12612,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:28:28.000Z","msg":"其實我無用過HKG+，甚至幾年都無上高登，係機緣巧合下先知最近高登發生咩事。但當我見到lihk獨立成為一個討論區時，嗰種感覺就好似搵返初戀一樣咁甜蜜同苦澀。<br />\n<br />\n我由做cd rom到用大學email做埋會員，一路都係用LIHK上高登，係我心目中LIHK其實已經同高登一樣，所有j圖、故仲有其他青春既回憶都係LIHK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但之後LIHK被block、膠登事件、仲有好多唔知得咩事，最慘係我唔記得左密碼，之後就無再上高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以今次見到LIHK自己變左做一個討論區，我就即刻諗辦法做會員，因為原來呢個充滿回憶既地方仲係到無變到，其實我黎LIHKG唔係因為HKG+，係因LIHK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIn LIHK， I love <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3705a38c78a1e983120dd78422e7d6b5e643ab90","tid":12612,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"Btw 原來搵isp email真係好撚難 搵左成日先搵到一個"},{"pid":"0883c1ecdbd0f15fc8da5f4880948c069f7d6c15","tid":12612,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:32:30.000Z","msg":"Btw LIHK好似好聽過LIHKG"},{"pid":"a81a4db865180d129340172986dec69ca78b21e6","tid":12612,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"推一推"}]}